import React from 'react';
import { Nav, Navbar, Button, NavDropdown, Col, Container } from 'react-bootstrap';
import styled from 'styled-components';
import './NavigationBar.scss';




export const NavigationBar = () => (
    <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" >
         {/* <Row className="d-flex justify-content-between"> */}
            <Col>
                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
                <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
                    <Nav className="ml-2">
                        <Nav.Link href="#features">HOME</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link href="#pricing">POSTS</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link href="#pricing">ABOUT</Nav.Link>
                    </Nav>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Col>

            <Col className="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <Navbar.Brand href="#home" className="m-0">MUSING FORWARD</Navbar.Brand>
            </Col>

            <Col>
                <form className="form-inline d-none d-lg-flex justify-content-end">
                    <button className="btn" type="button">Get Involved</button>
                </form>
            </Col>

        </Navbar>
)
